metadata.name: Euclidean #1
metadata.description: Euclidean Nodes is a high quality (4k) collection of 512 generative art NFT's on Ethereum Blockchain. Each node on the structure is randomly generated by the code and each node connected to the nearest one. Distances between each nodes are calculated by using Euclidean Distances Formula. That's why every design is different from another.In the process of creating Euclidean Nodes seed value is previous design' hash and the hash value is converted to a numeric value. So by that means all Euclidean Nodes are chained each other.
